mlink is an annex pointer.\r\n\r\nIt turns out that this has a real performance hit. In a repo with 33k files doing this increases the runtime of a `status()` from 4s to 12s.\r\n\r\nHowever, simply disabling this will impact the convenience-level felt in high-level code, as this was done to homogenize cross-platform/mode feel when dealing with annex'ed files.\r\n\r\nUsing pathlib would immediately gain 2s speedup (but see comment in code re PY3.5).\r\n\r\nSwitch to `os.readlink()` based test seems to be the obvious improvement: runtime ~5s\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "mih", "id": 136479, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEzNjQ3OQ==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/136479?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih", "html_url": "https://github.com/mih", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/3300/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/3300/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null}